title: Midara na Ao-chan wa Benkyou ga Dekinai (Ao-chan Can't Study!)
synopsis: Show them your A-O face! As an innocent child, Ao Horie would unhesitantly proclaim the origins of her name. Now that she is in high school, she is determined to study hard in order to one day escape the influence of her lascivious father, a famous erotic author. However, when the amiable Takumi Kijima confesses to Horie, her mind runs wild with scandalous thoughts.
